description:
In this video the long awaited Waldo visual ML cheat detection program is released in an alpha state. It works, and can be further trained by an average PC user with the friendly user interface. 

Go to https://SAN.com/basicallyhomeless to get better news only on the Straight Arrow News app and stay fully informed with Unbiased, Straight facts. 


Waldo links:
Download waldo - https://github.com/Mr-Homeless/waldo

Download the base model to use for training - https://huggingface.co/jinggu/jing-model/blob/main/vit_g_ps14_ak_ft_ckpt_7_clean.pth

Download my model that has already been trained on 1000~ clips - https://www.patreon.com/posts/139968535

Keep in mind, this model is tiny compared to what the final model will need to be. It is not yet the "know all" model.
